flowchart TB
  A["Person tries to use the app"]
  B["Request is for:<br/>1) Login<br/>or<br/>2) Change Password"]
  C["System keeps a short counter<br/>for the same person/session source"]
  D{"How many tries in the last 15 minutes?"}
  E["10 or fewer tries:<br/>Request is allowed"]
  F["11th try or more:<br/>Request is blocked"]
  G["Person sees message:<br/>Too many attempts. Please try again shortly."]
  H["System returns status 429<br/>(Too Many Requests)"]
  I["System also tells how long to wait"]
  J["After 15 minutes, counter resets"]
  K["Tries can work again"]
  L["Why this exists:<br/>Stops rapid repeated guessing<br/>and protects accounts"]

  A --> B --> C --> D
  D -- "10 or fewer" --> E
  D -- "11 or more" --> F --> G --> H --> I --> J --> K
  E --> L
  K --> L
